<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="reference_group">
<paragraph blockId="16.[151,1436,1015,1292]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<taxonomicName authority="Steindachner, 1881" authorityName="Steindachner" authorityYear="1881" box="[151,622,1051,1076]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chaetodontidae" genus="Chaetodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="hoefleri">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,622,1051,1076]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,379,1051,1076]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Chaetodon hoefleri</emphasis>
Steindachner, 
<number box="[566,622,1051,1076]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1881.0">1881</number>
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, was doubtfully reported from the central Mediterranean by 
<bibRefCitation author="Torchio" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refString="Torchio, M. (1968) Sulla eventuale presenza in acque mediterranee di individui dei generi Cephalopholis Bl. Schn, e Chaetodon L. (Pisces Osteichthyes). Natura, Milano, 59 (3 - 4), 210 - 213." type="journal article" year="1968">
Torchio (
<number box="[159,217,1087,1111]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1968.0">1968</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
on the basis of a specimen received from Professor A. Vatova. According to 
<bibRefCitation author="Tortonese" box="[1089,1281,1087,1111]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refString="Tortonese, E. (1975) Osteichthyes (Pesci ossei). Parte seconda. Fauna d'Italia. Vol. 11. Edizioni Calderini, Bologna, 636 pp." type="book" year="1975">
Tortonese (
<number box="[1215,1273,1087,1111]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1975.0">1975</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
all records of butterfly fishes in the Mediterranean, including old citations from the Adriatic as 
<taxonomicName box="[1062,1243,1124,1148]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chaetodontidae" genus="Chaetodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="octofasciatus">
<emphasis box="[1062,1243,1124,1148]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">C. octofasciatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1297,1388,1125,1148]" class="Actinopterygii" family="Chaetodontidae" genus="Chaetodon" kingdom="Animalia" order="Perciformes" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="niger">
<emphasis box="[1297,1388,1125,1148]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">C. niger</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, are to be considered doubtful due to the lack of habitat 
<typeStatus box="[748,796,1161,1185]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">type</typeStatus>
(i.e. coral reefs) required by these fishes. Nevertheless, 
<bibRefCitation author="Monod" box="[151,314,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refString="Monod, T. (1979) Chaetodontidae. In: Hureau, J. C. &amp; Monod, T. (Eds.), Check-list of the fishes of the North-eastern Atlantic and of the Mediterranean (Clofnam). Vol. 1. Unesco, Paris, pp. 422 - 423." type="book" year="1979">
Monod (
<number box="[248,306,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1979.0">1979</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
mentions a living specimen taken at Les Goudes, near Marseille on 
<date box="[1096,1207,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1959-07">
July 
<number box="[1151,1207,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1959.0">1959</number>
</date>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Nalbant" box="[1264,1436,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refString="Nalbant, T. (1986) Chaetodontidae. In: Whitehead, P. J. P., Bauchot, M. L., Hureau, J. C., Nielsen, J. &amp; Tortonese, E. (Eds.), Fishes of the North-eastern Atlantic and the Mediterranean. Vol. 2. Unesco, Paris, pp. 914 - 915." type="book" year="1986">
Nalbant (
<number box="[1369,1427,1196,1220]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="1986.0">1986</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
confirms the presence, although sporadic, of the species in the western Mediterranean. It is not included in the lists of Golani 
<emphasis box="[264,314,1268,1292]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number box="[335,394,1268,1292]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="2002.0">2002</number>
) and of 
<bibRefCitation box="[487,723,1268,1292]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" refString="Zenetos, A., Gofas, S., Verlaque, M. Cinar, M. E., Garcia Raso, J. E., et al. (2010) Alien species in the Mediterranean Sea by 2010. A contribution to the application of European Union's Strategy Framework Directive (MSFD). Part I. Spatial distribution. Mediterranean Marine Science, 11 (2), 381 - 493." type="journal article">
Zenetos 
<emphasis box="[582,632,1268,1292]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">et al</emphasis>
. (
<number box="[654,716,1268,1292]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" value="2010.0">2010</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
